version 0.3.1 (6-May-2006):
	* Fixed a bug where libleaftag couldn't pass the configure stage if
	  libcheck wasn't installed.
	* Fixed a runtime warning sometimes caused when untagging.
	* Added API documentation.
	* Added thread safety support. This fixes bug #6.
	* Changed lt_uri_normalize() to strip trailing slashes. This may require
	  that some people export and re-import their database using tagutils, to
	  fix any existing entries. This closes bug #7.

version 0.3.0 (15-February-2006):
	* Initial public release.
